      "Pot 2: ",
      "Phaser modulation linearization test.",
      "Sine LFO (left) and Ramp/Triangle LFO (right) each shaped via LOG/EXP power-law then mapped to all-pass coefficient range. Mixer 2:1 selects between them (Gain1=sine, Gain2=triangle). Adjust LOG multiplier (default 0.5=sqrt) for more/less curve correction. Final Scale/Offset sets sweep range [0.80, 0.94]."
    ]
